author: Scott Leonardson
title: Scott Leonardson
text: From the moment Lisa called me at the exact time of our appointment, she was very gregarious and knowledgeable on how to set up everything with my LLC. This process was so streamlined I have no idea why anyone would go anywhere else to set up their business entities. I am not sure how long Lisa has been with the company, but she seems like a seasoned pro to me and should get a raise in pay!!
